WEBVTT

00:01.162 --> 00:02.767
The lost Smurf village!

00:02.833 --> 00:04.338
It's time to take a road trip.

00:04.885 --> 00:06.993
I'll be all like, "Argh!"

00:07.111 --> 00:08.733
And they'll be all like, "Oh no!"

00:08.821 --> 00:10.309
And I'll be like...

00:13.154 --> 00:15.912
I think my glasses are coming off.

00:18.437 --> 00:18.939
What's so funny?

00:18.995 --> 00:21.105
That's what I call talking out of your butt!

00:22.037 --> 00:24.215
We have to find the village before they do.

00:24.289 --> 00:25.954
Incoming bird!

00:31.961 --> 00:32.695
Oh boy.

00:36.436 --> 00:39.457
We mean you no harm, we're looking for the lost village.

00:45.317 --> 00:45.670
What the...

00:46.059 --> 00:48.761
I'm really freaking out, you guys!

00:49.232 --> 00:51.160
Smurfs: The Lost Village.

